name: Camden Election Fallout
description:
This game is built in collaboration with Alvin Inc. and based on his latest ACNH island, Camden. Go ahead and check out this island tour video where this game was first announced!

Music track from study with blathers by demongummies, used with their permission.

Any donations on this game are shared between Spirit of the Raccoon and Alvin Inc., and will enable us to continue to create games!
